message: Police netted 11 as a result of a "Human Trafficking Demand Reduction Operation" that attracted hundreds of men looking to buy sexual services. The one-day operation pulled in 282 potential clients, who responded to false prostitution advertisements set up by Fort Collins police. https://buff.ly/2LVHSbf
